        <ArticleTitle>Call to Action: Structural Racism as a Fundamental Driver of Health Disparities: A Presidential Advisory From the American Heart Association.</ArticleTitle>
        <Pagination>
          <StartPage>e454</StartPage>
          <EndPage>e468</EndPage>
